snippet.title: Voltaire the Vegan Vampire - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
An action-farming-roguelite, full of whimsical flora and mischievous creatures! Dracula's lastborn, Voltaire, has decided to swap human flesh for ~*plant flesh*~ to satisfy his dark cravings.
